### Standalone-server request collection.
###
### Designed for the VS Code REST Client extension. Replace the
### @adminKey + @tenantKey values once you've extracted them from the
### server's responses.

@host = http://localhost:3000
@adminKey = YOUR_ADMIN_KEY_FROM_DOT_ENV
@tenantKey = zts_live_acme_REPLACE_AFTER_ISSUE
@tenantRef = acme

### Liveness
GET {{host}}/healthz

### Readiness (DB ping)
GET {{host}}/readyz

### Register tenant
POST {{host}}/v1/tenants
Authorization: Bearer {{adminKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantRef": "{{tenantRef}}",
  "vatNumber": "301234567890003",
  "egsUuid": "00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001",
  "vatName": "Acme Trading Co.",
  "crn": "1010010101",
  "branchName": "Riyadh HQ",
  "branchIndustry": "Retail",
  "location": {
    "cityName": "Riyadh",
    "citySubdivision": "Olaya",
    "street": "King Fahd Rd",
    "plotIdentification": "1234",
    "building": "5678",
    "postalZone": "12345"
  },
  "environment": "simulation"
}

### Onboard the tenant (blocks 30-90s)
POST {{host}}/v1/tenants/{{tenantRef}}/onboard
Authorization: Bearer {{adminKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "otp": "REPLACE_WITH_FATOORA_OTP",
  "solutionName": "My Solution v1.0",
  "environment": "simulation"
}

### Inspect tenant status + per-scenario progress
GET {{host}}/v1/tenants/{{tenantRef}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminKey}}

### Issue a tenant API key (token shown ONCE)
POST {{host}}/v1/tenants/{{tenantRef}}/api-keys
Authorization: Bearer {{adminKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "label": "pos-1" }

### Issue a simplified tax invoice (uses tenant bearer)
POST {{host}}/v1/tenants/{{tenantRef}}/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantKey}}
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: invoice-2026-05-17-001

{
  "input": {
    "kind": "simplified-tax-invoice",
    "issueDate": "2026-05-17",
    "issueTime": "12:00:00",
    "buyerName": "Walk-in customer",
    "lineItems": [
      { "id": "1", "name": "Latte 250ml", "quantity": 1, "taxExclusivePrice": 12, "vatPercent": 15 }
    ]
  },
  "submit": true
}

### Load a persisted invoice
GET {{host}}/v1/tenants/{{tenantRef}}/invoices/REPLACE_WITH_INVOICE_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantKey}}

### List tenants (admin view, no secrets)
GET {{host}}/v1/tenants?environment=simulation
Authorization: Bearer {{adminKey}}

### Prometheus metrics
GET {{host}}/metrics
